I"t<h1 id="dropdown">Dropdown</h1>

<p>Use select to let users select from a long list. As some users can struggle this functionality, only use as a last resort.</p>

<div class="form">
  <div class="group">
    <label for="sorting" class="form-hint">Sort by</label>
    <select class="form-control" id="sorting" name="sorting">
      <option>Recently published</option>
      <option selected="">Recently updated</option>
      <option>Most views</option>
      <option>Most comments</option>
    </select>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;div class="form"&gt;
  &lt;div class="group"&gt;
