<h2 id="how-to-use-select">How to use select</h2>

<p>Try using the <a href="/essex-county-council-digital-manual/Design-system/Elements-and-Components/radio">radio</a> or <a href="/essex-county-council-digital-manual/Design-system/Elements-and-Components/checkbox">checkbox</a> elements instead.</p>

<p>It’s often used when there is a long list that can’t presented in another way, such as a list of countries or languages.</p>

